{"tid":423950,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"24hrs Minecraft Relaxing Survival Server 1.12 *whitelist 隨緣招生","createTime":"2017-10-04T10:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T15:27:10.000Z","uid":21749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6604e38c90d7558e8d155fea53a177ba613310d0","tid":423950,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"版本: 1.12 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">IP &darr;</span></span> <br />\nkinglam.mcph.eu <br />\n<br />\n加whitelist(白名單), 係post留game名 或 入Discord講底個game名:<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Discord:</span></span> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Ft9yDcvG&d=dxc1uezZ%2FGoTHL6prBmJHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c9c7f343\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/t9yDcvG</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Server 設定 &amp; 規則</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無規則, 無防火, 無防爆</span> (除左creeper唔爆, 其他都會爆)<br />\n有領地插件 (教學: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QIl-kvLYscA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQIl-kvLYscA&d=dxc1uezZ%2FGoTHL6prBmJHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e2b2331b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QIl-kvLYscA</a> )<br />\n木牌鎖箱<br />\nlift  升降機 (教學: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxUPo3Dm5L8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqxUPo3Dm5L8&d=dxc1uezZ%2FGoTHL6prBmJHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2eedfdad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxUPo3Dm5L8</a>)<br />\n商店 (入面有少量建築材料可買, 貨幣係 黑曜石同地獄石)<br />\n有創造世界<br />\n有線上地圖 (網址放左係DISCORD群入面)<br />\n要用飛行同X-RAY透視個D, 唔該自己搞掂, 唔好問我拎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">一般指令</span></span><br />\n/sethome NAME 可以設置2個家 (例如: /sethome abc 之後 /home abc 就OK)<br />\n/home 回家<br />\n/back 返回上一次死亡/傳送的位置<br />\n/tpa NAME  傳送到其他玩家身邊<br />\n/hat  將手上面既物品笠係個頭度做裝飾<br />\n/co i  查看被破壞或被偷竊記錄, 然後搵佢找數<br />\n/mutechat 關閉文字頻道<br />\n/bal      查看身上擁有的money<br />\n/money 查看身上擁有的money<br />\n/help   查看其他可用的指令<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Server 狀況</span></span><br />\n已經開左超過半年到而加, 將會至少開到出年暑假前(6月左右),<br />\n依半年經過好多次既SETTING測試, 變動同檢討, 到而加既最終SETTING,<br />\n規則方面由好多麻煩規則同設定到而加既無規則自由奔放,<br />\nServer地圖一直用緊個張圖無轉過, 只係終界同地獄RESET左,<br />\n唯一管理員(無其他ADMIN了) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">出生點, 有保護, 防止被殺, 洗傳點 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://na.cx/i/CZ3gisH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZ3gisH.jpg&h=7fd974ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊POST 6: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/382161/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/382161/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 5: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/302902/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/302902/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 4: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/204927/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/204927/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 3: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/165476/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/165476/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 2: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/124427/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/124427/page/1</a><br />\n舊POST 1: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/101334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/101334/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c8eb8e19a5755247425bfb4c80341491f9af4038","tid":423950,"uid":21749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">另隨POST附上 開心版 安裝教學 及 下載點:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">開心版 安裝教學 </span></span><br /